content_vision: You live in denial. Do you ever feel that the world is full of lies and deceptio? We like to see the world burning.
text:
Intro:
we up in this game, ain't no way down
we hop out fresh, we run this town.

Verse 1:
you can't keep your word, it's all over the place,
now you see the consequences in that temple space.
i'll never stumble, even in the toughest fight,
your words can't hurt me, i know i'm doin' what's right.
you ain't even aware, lost in your own world,
obviously oblivious, let's take a walk, girl.
i'm coming through the door, no need for keys,
and all i see is these grills shining, gold teeth.

Pre-Chorus 1:
if i think too much i might just go crazy,
got an ak banana clip, ready to spray- z the haters who tryna play me.

Chorus 1:
grab a bottle of moscato, let's unwind,
'cause in this moment, nothing else matters in our minds.
i used to be down on my luck, now i'm living large,
and when them north winds howl, i'm still in charge.

Verse 2:
cause i'm styling on you, showing off these shoes
but we must be the fools, always chasing the blues.
if my momma ever found out what i did on vacay,
you know we're only good for one thing, that's the nighttime way.
if you give me your rent for the month,
i'll make sure you living lavish like a dogghouse nigga, gettin' all the blunts.
hoe death, hear the death knell ring,
hellcat, my ride's a deadly thing.

Pre-Chorus 2:
sticky situation, like peanut butter jelly time,
kim never gave me a kiss, but i'm feeling fine.

Chorus 2:
we don't need no excuse, we gonna party long and hard,
tunechi knew what's up, now it's time to suck on this tar.
everyday's a hustle, gotta stay on top,
but you know my gun doesn't stop.

Bridge:
can't take it anymore, gotta release the tension,
hop in the ride and we'll find a new dimension.
feeling uptight now, gotta shake off this funk,
got the streets hot, every corner, every nook.

Outro:
i wanna get invited, break into that party,
maybe even travel all the way to poland, in a hurry.

Instrumental:
the years can be our enemies, always dragging us down
but who's gonna make you a big, help you wear the crown.

active_struct.name: The Groovy Breakdown
attrs: starts with a strong intro that grabs the listener's attention
has a simple and easy to follow structure with a verse, prechorus, chorus, and bridge sequence
includes an instrumental section for added musical appeal

struct_suggs.name: The Climactic Change-Up
attrs: includes a prechorus that adds tension and anticipation before the chorus
builds up to a final climax with the addition of a bridge
allows for multiple chorus variations throughout the song
has a strong outro that leaves a lasting impression on the listener

struct_suggs.name: The Progressive Reprise
attrs: has a simple but effective structure with repeating verses and choruses
includes a bridge for added variety
suitable for songs with a clear and concise message
can be easily customized to fit different genres and styles

struct_suggs.name: The Instrumental Interlude
attrs: allows for a gradual build up, with an intro, verse, prechorus, and chorus sequence
includes an instrumental section to showcase musical talents or add a break in the vocals
has a bridge that propels the song towards a strong finish in the outro
commonly used in pop and rock songs

struct_suggs.name: The Dynamic Loop
attrs: has a familiar structure that is well-known to listeners
includes a repeating chorus for an ear-catching hook
allows for variations in the prechorus to keep the song interesting
can be used for emotional and impactful songs

struct_suggs.name: The Unexpected Shift
attrs: includes an intro that sets the tone for the song

struct_suggs.name: The Instrumental Finale

struct_suggs.name: The Harmonious Contrast
attrs: includes an intro, verse, and prechorus before the first chorus
builds up to a climactic bridge before the final chorus in the outro
suitable for songs with a strong emotional message or storyline
